item.title: Contact 03
item.dc:creator: Don Pixel
item.content:encoded:
Hello, Nice to Hear from You!

I am Laura Kelley, Photographer and Founder of Photberry. To create modern recognizable stuff I am working with a strong network of experienced professionals. My approach is to develop unique pictures and reveal your individual look by inspiring each other in permanent new collaborations with different talents.

I work with established agencies, labels and organizations, as well as young talents and startups. I set up teams to shape your identity, push your idea and manage the workflow from pre- to post-production. My focus is on commercial, fashion, music, portrait & editorial productions.

I was brought to work with

Nike - Dior - Nespresso - Disney - Guerlain - Celine - Chanel - AXA - Thierry Mugler - Le Meurice Lancel - Nivea - Bosh - Dargaud - NRJ - Baccarat - Casio - Yard Paper & more.

Phone: +1 (800) 456 37 96

Email: info@photberry.com

Facebook-f Twitter Behance Pinterest

We Are Artists Hungry for Quality in Aesthetics

Play Video

Our Services

Our approach is to develop unique pictures and reveal your individual look by inspiring each other in permanent new collaborations with different talents. We set up teams to shape your identity, push your idea and manage the workflow from pre- to post-production. Our focus is on commercial, fashion, music, portrait & editorial productions.

Commercial Production

Donec pretium tristique felis vel venenatis. Orci varius natoq penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridicul mus.

Fashion Production

Nam dolor mauris, finibus nec efficitur et, facilisis id arcu. Sed condimentum dapibus tortor, quis efficitur erat sagittis at magna.

Music Production

Commodo est, id condimentum est dolor sed purus. Suspe dignissim facilisis augue. Mauris cursus lobortis viverra cing elit.

Portrait Production

Etiam tristique vulputate erat vel tincidunt. Morbi risus tellu, condimentum at nunc vitae, consectetur tempor velit dapibus.

item.title: About 01
item.dc:creator: Don Pixel
item.content:encoded:
Welcome to Our Photo Studio

We are a creative collective of three freelance artists hungry for quality in aesthetics. To create modern recognizable stuff we are working with a strong network of experienced professionals. Our approach is to develop unique pictures and reveal your individual look by inspiring each other in permanent new collaborations with different talents. We work with established agencies, labels and organizations, as well as young talents and startups. We set up teams to shape your identity, push your idea and manage the workflow from pre- to post-production. Our focus is on commercial, fashion, music, portrait & editorial productions.

item.title: About 03
item.dc:creator: Don Pixel
item.content:encoded:
Welcome to Our Photo Studio

We are a creative collective of three freelance artists hungry for quality in aesthetics. To create modern recognizable stuff we are working with a strong network of experienced professionals. Our approach is to develop unique pictures and reveal your individual look by inspiring each other in permanent new collaborations with different talents. We work with established agencies, labels and organizations, as well as young talents and startups. We set up teams to shape your identity, push your idea and manage the workflow from pre- to post-production. Our focus is on commercial, fashion, music, portrait & editorial productions.
